(42, 17, 23, 42, 17, 21, 21, 'see here; or, see there', 'Connection of Kingdom of God', 'Both passages emphasize the idea of seeking the kingdom of God. The SOURCE verse warns against following external claims, while the TARGET passage asserts that the kingdom is within individuals.', 'theme', 0.32799999999999996, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
